#: ../../library/readline.rst:131
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Save the history list to a readline history file, overwriting any existing "
"file.  The default filename is :file:`~/.history`.  This calls "
":c:func:`!write_history` in the underlying library and raises an "
":ref:`auditing event <auditing>` ``open`` with the file name if given and "
